 aiming their tanks and firing an arsenal of weapons at\neach other across randomly generated destructible terrain. Judge the angle,\npower, and wind to land your shots — there's no trajectory preview, so every\nshot is a test of skill and intuition.\n\n16 weapons including nukes, MIRVs, lasers, and chain reaction inducers.\n3 defense systems: shields, inertia dampeners, and repulsers.\n6 wall types, 5 wind levels, destructible terrain with crumbling.\nLocal 2-player hot-seat and online multiplayer via Firebase.\n\nFree and open source. No ads. No tracking. No in-app purchases.\n"}, "preferredSigner": "dd7e16bf9c9cd5b2a74160a39a12ce41775243e3d5b8b9bca5585ac4050f245e"}, "versions": {"21ed51750e14ce1ff9b1349a1c214eb6d48198e73b62ef35b0fd0990c525ab5f": {"added": 1775035223000, "file": {"name": "/TankWars-v1.1.0.apk", "sha256": "21ed51750e14ce1ff9b1349a1c214eb6d48198e73b62ef35b0fd0990c525ab5f", "size": 3435850}, "manifest": {"versionName": "1.1.0", "versionCode": 110, "usesSdk": {"minSdkVersion": 24, "targetSdkVersion": 36}, "signer": {"sha256": ["dd7e16bf9c9cd5b2a74160a39a12ce41775243e3d5b8b9bca5585ac4050f245e"]}, "usesPermission": [{"name": "android.permission.INTERNET"}, {"name": "com.tankwars.mobile.DYNAMIC_RECEIVER_NOT_EXPORTED_PERMISSION"}]}}, "bf94571ef465278e4af93f78868241a9f68890224526ef513bab2837d43e1d9c": {"added": 1775030525000, "file": {"name": "/TankWars-v1.0.0.apk", "sha256": "bf94571ef465278e4af93f78868241a9f68890224526ef513bab2837d43e1d9c", "size": 3435850}, "manifest": {"versionName": "1.0", "versionCode": 1, "usesSdk": {"minSdkVersion": 24, "targetSdkVersion": 36}, "signer": {"sha256": ["dd7e16bf9c9cd5b2a74160a39a12ce41775243e3d5b8b9bca5585ac4050f245e"]}, "usesPermission": [{"name": "android.permission.INTERNET"}, {"name": "com.tankwars.mobile.DYNAMIC_RECEIVER_NOT_EXPORTED_PERMISSION"}]}}}}, "dev.wath.openlibeextendedeinkremix": {"metadata": {"icon": {"en-US": {"name": "/icons/dev.wath.openlibeextendedeinkremix.2014.png", "sha256": "c7c0c0189145e4e32a4